				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/02/26/1639-je-taime-etat-maman-surtout-tes-kicks-dans-les-parties?replytocom=11275#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-11275", "11275", "respond", "1639")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
