				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/02/26/1639-je-taime-etat-maman-surtout-tes-kicks-dans-les-parties?replytocom=11777#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-11777", "11777", "respond", "1639")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
